```{r ampulla 32590886, include=FALSE}

PMID_32590886 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32590886', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32590886 <- paste0(PMID_32590886$journal,' ', PMID_32590886$year, ' ', PMID_32590886$month,';', PMID_32590886$volume,'(', PMID_32590886$number,'):', PMID_32590886$pages)

PubMed_32590886 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32590886$eprint)

doi_32590886 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32590886$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
